{"tid":766102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盛傳容海恩懷孕　被問點睇婚前性行為　葉太：今時今日「Very common」","createTime":"2018-08-03T10:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T10:40:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15fcc50a524f7d9ca8768f3dc18a3a256e5a9f1a","tid":766102,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180803/s00001/f5835e41fa8cb1892907ceb3af02fdac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180803%2Fs00001%2Ff5835e41fa8cb1892907ceb3af02fdac.jpg&h=e6471f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新民黨立法會議員容海恩（Eunice），據指今個月就會同該黨嘅政策總裁袁彌昌（Derek）拉埋天窗，成為立法會首名任內結婚嘅女議員，政圈更盛傳佢雙喜臨門，有咗BB。Eunice日前同黨主席葉劉淑儀等人，與特首林鄭月娥會面提交《施政報告》建議之後，仲喺facebook上載咗幾張相，不過網民焦點依照落係Eunice身上。<br />\n<br />\n當日以平底鞋同黑色西裝外套打扮現身嘅Eunice，未有回應記者係咪好快做媽媽嘅提問。一眾網民之後就喺葉太嘅facebook留言：「有冇幫手改名呀」，又話Eunice似乎用手擋住個肚。當有人問：「葉太對婚前性行為有乜睇法」個陣，葉太更喺帖文發表唯一嘅回覆指「Very common these days」，形容今時今日都好普遍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180803/s00001/1533286153881\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180803%2Fs00001%2F1533286153881&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b38f9ed4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180803%2Fs00001%2F1533286153881&h=8a1559fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180803/s00001/1533286153881</a>"},{"pid":"0c91ccb3e2c334d182a3bd1cebb4e05edcfa02b2","tid":766102,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:32:02.000Z","msg":"如果佢個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1d3f0332c1a39f90e61929694c51b3ec604156","tid":766102,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0c91ccb3e2c334d182a3bd1cebb4e05edcfa02b2","tid":766102,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:32:02.000Z","msg":"如果佢個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"佢個女好安全"},{"pid":"ce710f4c1fe80d0a1a3612f2eb7137b3dea33492","tid":766102,"uid":177475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:40:07.000Z","msg":"我覺得議會内外唔應該牽涉太多性事"}]}